This paper is about image captioning, which is a task related to computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The proposed method involves using attention mechanisms, which is a common technique in deep learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the use of LSTMs, which are a type of neural network commonly used in natural language processing and machine learning (cs.AI). Finally, the paper evaluates its method using various metrics, which is related to information retrieval (cs.IR).
